remental analytics. Furthermore, the CEO mandated 100% feature parity, meaning no filters could be removed, regardless of how rarely they were used. Timeline: 4 months, single-release redesign. Partners: CEO, Director of Product, PM, Engineering."]}]]}],"$L4"]}]}],"$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb","$Lc","$Ld","$Le","$Lf"]}],"$L10"]}]}],"$L11"]}],["$L12","$L13"],"$L14"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
